title: Family Vacation - Madrid - Part 1/2
description:
The Arnette Skateboarding team travels to Spain to spend a few days exploring the streets of Madrid.
Featuring Pat Duffy, Scott Decenzo, Javier Sarmiento, Sierra Fellers, Cristian Sanchez, Willy Santos, Alain Goikoetxea, Danny Leon, and Fries Tallieu.
